title: Trend Reznor 2/8: M Night Shymalan, Hannah Montana, Bitcoin, Kevin Garnett, Gorilla Glue

On this edition of Trend Reznor Jack and Miles discuss a new M Night Shymalan movie coming out called "Old", Miley Cyrus' Super Bowl performance, Tesla buying $1.5B in Bitcoin skyrocketing the value, Kevin Garnett saying Basketball has changed and is more "saucy" now, and updates from Gorilla Glue Hair Girl.
